10/17/81	subroutine_usage.compin

Syntax:  .ifi subroutine_usage
     OR  .ifi subr_usage


Function:
This macro emits an subroutine usage syntax label and prepares for dec-
laration and call usage lines.


Macro action:
1) inserts 24pt. of white space
2) emits the label "USAGE SYNTAX" in 10pt Helvetica Bold Italic flush
   left, followed by white space appropriate for the device
3) sets the text indentation to the second level in preparation for the
   declaration and call syntax lines (see subroutine_entry.compin.info
   concerning generation of the declaration and call syntax lines).

(END)
